{"tid":1673322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰隆尼亞絕對係香港人既模仿對象，同時係呢次事件既反思","createTime":"2019-10-24T14:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T12:35:12.000Z","uid":36092,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d1ede362265c854fa4240c5cf1e02c5f6c22f9","tid":1673322,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"我而家係到屌柒你班垃圾風向狗+熱青城垃圾信徒，人地一黎就係甘願站係香港人果邊同中國交惡，你地就屌柒人地再加「窩裏反」，中左離間計互屌。人地有冇割蓆呀？人地遠在西方都支持香港到呢個地步呀？我地又幾可唱過加泰歌，fing加泰旗？連去集會都要比熱青城+連登風向撚及幼兒屌一大輪，笑人加泰狗呀？你班撚樣痾篤尿照下鏡啦，我唔理你地想獨立定自治好，學下人地一條心好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n你地仲戇鳩到信埋陳雲果套垃圾國際倫理覺得會影響到人權法，屈人收中共錢又屈人係共產黨，成班傻閪冇撚讀過書唔識國際關係人云亦云。<br />\n<br />\n你覺得你地唔支持加泰，就可以乜撚都唔做比美國佬打救咩？人地90幾%決定獨立，就係呢一點就構建到佢地係一個民族、一個國家既基礎，香港人有冇呀？"},{"pid":"3dc240f9597e01c0930acc5f6a1a36923318a4ee","tid":1673322,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCA3VqG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCA3VqG.jpg&h=1b492863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=b7e71706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a983433616dd438e20c5cb8807dda3e80a5b2944","tid":1673322,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecfaf86a43c95e3f848bb8ad94ed6d4ce287ff8","tid":1673322,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"推到cc台啲傻西見到"},{"pid":"7b15df8b217b2df8d83ade8860b373e2e975a4e2","tid":1673322,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:54:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b50f6ed4971ec4f60efa23f7b36347a9f5cd7c0","tid":1673322,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"